name: Gustave Courbet's The Desperate Man by Zaam
description: Le Désespéré is an 1843-1845 oil on canvas self-portrait by Gustave Courbet, produced early during his stay in Paris.  This project is a recreation of Courbet’s self portrait depicting morphing of identity when changed and replicated by people to better fit in. Created with the help of Artificial Intelligence. This is a unique and single edition work 1/1
